  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The use of prophylactic treatment with vitamin c may prevent complex regional pain syndrome
      (CRPS)
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      There are several studies similar in wrist fracture.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
